OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779264378
OL,3,CNew CCTV shows attempted murder
OL,4,Csuspect moments after man in 60s
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FPolice officers investigating an
OL,8,Fattempted murder in Stafford have
OL,9,Freleased CCTV footage of a man thought
OL,10,Fto be the suspect.
OL,12,FOne piece of footage shows the man
OL,13,Fbefore the attack at around 6.36pm on
OL,14,FThursday 14 May, while another video
OL,15,Fwas recorded in the Castlefields area
OL,16,Fof the town at around 7pm, shortly
OL,17,Fafter a man in his 60s was stabbed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
