OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779264378
OL,3,CNew CCTV shows attempted murder
OL,4,Csuspect moments after man in 60s
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FIn a statement, Staffordshire Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "His behaviour at the time is
OL,9,Fsignificant as he was seen running
OL,10,Faway from the scene.
OL,12,F"If you recognise him or saw anything
OL,13,Fthat evening, please get in touch.
OL,14,FWe're also asking you to think
OL,15,Fcarefully about anyone you know who
OL,16,Fmay have returned home with
OL,17,Funexplained injuries or whose
OL,18,Fbehaviour has been out of character."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
