PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779264378
OL,3,CNew CCTV shows attempted murder
OL,4,Csuspect moments after man in 60s
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FPolice were called to Newport Road at
OL,8,F7pm on Thursday, close to the Castle
OL,9,FGolf and Leisure, following reports of
OL,10,Fviolence.
OL,12,FA man in his 60s was found on a bench
OL,13,Fnear the town centre after the attack
OL,14,Fby a member of the public. The victim,
OL,15,Fa man in his 60s, remains in critical
OL,16,Fcondition, but stable condition in
OL,17,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
