PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779264378
OL,3,CNew CCTV shows attempted murder
OL,4,Csuspect moments after man in 60s
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Ian
OL,8,FFitzgerald said: "Our investigation is
OL,9,Fmoving at pace, and I want to thank
OL,10,Fthose members of the public who have
OL,11,Falready helped us. The clearer CCTV we
OL,12,Fare releasing today was provided
OL,13,Fbecause of earlier appeals, which
OL,14,Fshows the real difference the
OL,15,Fcommunity can make.
OL,17,F"But we still need your help to
OL,18,Fidentify the man and would ask anyone
OL,19,Fwho recognises him to get in touch as
OL,20,Feven the smallest detail could prove
OL,21,Fsignificant.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
