CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1779264378
OL,3,CNew CCTV shows attempted murder
OL,4,Csuspect moments after man in 60s
OL,5,Cstabbed
OL,7,F"We understand the impact this violent
OL,8,Fattack has had within the community
OL,9,Fand that it can impact feelings of
OL,10,Fsafety. Local officers remain in the
OL,11,Farea to offer support, and the scene
OL,12,Fremains in place as a specialist
OL,13,Fsearch team continue their work."
OL,15,FThere has been an increased police
OL,16,Fpresence in the Castlefields area and
OL,17,Fsurrounding neighbourhoods, since the
OL,18,Fattack.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@aO]
